Class NamedElement

java.lang.Object
org.ontouml.model.OntoumlElement
org.ontouml.model.NamedElement
Direct Known Subclasses:
Diagram, ModelElement, Project
public abstract class NamedElement extends OntoumlElement
An identified element of an OntoUML ontology according to the OntoUML Metamodel, which includes projects, model elements, diagrams, views, and shapes.
